snippet.title: Angry Birds Seasons - Summer Pignic
snippet.description:
Get Ready for Angry Birds Seasons - Summer Pignic! The pesky pigs never break for holidays, and it's up to you to save the Angry Birds' eggs! Follow the RovioMobile channel for a special summer surprise coming soon!

Get Angry Birds Seasons:

- Download for iPhone or iPod Touch: http://bit.ly/k2rKEs
- Download for iPad http://bit.ly/iI74pn
- Download for Symbian^3: http://bit.ly/hzYCAr
- Download for Palm WebOS: http://bit.ly/fG9vXC
